      "And just like that, it’s the second-to-last week and we’re already on the giallo movies.  The first one has one of those strange titles like so many gialli.  Unfortunately, this one doesn’t stack up very well with the others, mainly because it really has very little horror or kills.  It’s really more of a thriller, some psychological, but really just a story of mystery and betrayal.  For that, it’s fine.. but for me, hoping for the typical mystery killer with black gloves type of movie.. it’s a little disappointing.  But oh well, this is just the warm-up for the week so, hopefully, next movie, we’ll really get into the swing of things.",
