      "I thought this might be one of those jungle island type movies, but it ended up being more of a haunted house movie, though not supernatural.  A group of guys make up a treasure hunting business and travel out to an island, bringing a woman and her.. friend?  The island has a big castle type place and people on the treasure hunting trip are dying one by one.  It’s mostly fun.. isolated mansion/castle on an island with a killer.  There are some typical old cheesy/cartoonish moments that you might expect from movies as old as this.  Again, it’s only 60 minutes, so it’s a quick watch.  Although, it did seem like it took a bit too much time to actually get to the island.. when you only have 60 minutes, you gotta get to that island quick.",
