      "One more bonus supernatural movie to finish out Week 6.  Amityville 3D is kind of the same old thing to start but instead of going down the religious route like in part 2, this one ends up going towards paranormal investigation.  I had fun with that part, as cheesy as it was.. but the rest of the movie was kind of slow leading up to that.  Unfortunately, I wasn’t able to watch this in 3D, otherwise who knows, maybe it’s the best movie ever made.. but as it stands in 2D, it was pretty average with a few highlights.",
      "5.5/10",
