      "This movie had the feel of a Twilight Zone episode, but three times as long.  If it were condensed into a 20-25 minute episode, it’d be all right.  Stretched out even at just over an hour, it drags a bit.  Kind of a fun cheesy concept and one of those titles that could apply to about any horror movie.  The flashback scene was pretty cool and I would have been on board with more flashback scenes like that, but oh well… we don’t always get what we want.",
