      "Well we’re back to “blood of”.  This was kind of bland but more “movie-like” than the last couple.  The horror aspect of it was pretty light, really just some killer chasing people but in more of an action way, not a suspenseful horror way.  So it’s ok as a movie, not really great, but it’s basically the kind of movie you’d see on MST3K and not much more.",
      "4.5/10",
      "And that’s that for the five Al Adamson movies for week 4.  I guess I got what I expected..",
