      "Bonus time week 2, here we go.  I’ve heard about this one as being one of those early examples of “meta” horror movies, sort of like <strong>Scream (1996)</strong>.  This one has more to do with b-movies from the 50s-70s where fictional movies from those eras are being shown at a “horrorthon”.  It’s a little bit like <strong>Matinee (1993)</strong> in some ways, though I liked that Matinee a bit more (which is not a horror movie, just about those old school gimmicky horror movies).  Anyway, this is pretty fun for the horrorthon atmosphere.. I’d love to go something like that in real life.  Minus the murder.",
