      "This is a little more the “90s” vibe I was expecting.  I went into it thinking it would be another one of those “group of spaceship crew fights off alien creatures” but it was actually a bit different.  Mainly, it was one alien creature loose in LA.  It starts in a kind of Stranger Things way with a young girl escaping a lab and trying to assimilate into the normal world.  Pretty entertaining movie, but I don’t really get the point of the “empath” character.. was he psychic or what..?  In spite of these small problems with the characters, I still enjoyed my time with it.",
